# Publish to TestFlight

## User Review Required
> [!NOTE]
> I will generate the `.ipa` file. You will need to upload this file using the Apple **Transporter** app or via **Xcode**.

## Proposed Changes
### Build Process
- Run `flutter clean` to remove cached build artifacts.
- Run `flutter pub get` to fetch dependencies.
- Run `pod install` in `ios/` directory to ensure native dependencies are linked.
- Run `flutter build ipa --release` to generate the uploadable archive.

## Verification Plan
